The licenses granted in this Section 2 are subject to the following
condition and limitation.

2.2. Contributor's Patent License to You

If You bring a patent infringement claim against a Contributor with respect
to a patent Licensable by such Contributor, then the patent licenses granted
by that Contributor to You under this License for that Contributor's
Contributions shall terminate as of the date such claim is filed.

2.3. Distribution of Source Form

All distribution of Covered Software in Source Code Form, including any
Modifications that You make or to which You contribute, must be under the
terms of this License. You must inform recipients that the Source Code Form
of the Covered Software is governed by the terms of this License, and how to
obtain a copy of this License. You may not offer or impose any terms on any
one that alters or restricts the applicable version of this License or the
rights granted hereunder to a recipient of Covered Software in Source Code
Form.

2.4. Distribution of Executable Form

If You distribute Covered Software in Executable Form then:

(a) such Covered Software must also be made available in Source Code Form,
as described in Section 2.3, and you must inform recipients of the
Executable Form how to obtain a copy of such Source Code Form by
reasonable means in a timely manner, at a charge no more than the cost of
distribution to the recipient; and

(b) you may distribute the Executable Form under the terms of this License,
or sublicense the Executable Form under different terms provided that the
license for the Executable Form does not attempt to limit or alter the
recipients' rights in the Source Code Form under this License.

2.5. Larger Works

You may create and distribute a Larger Work under terms of your choice, so
long as You do not attempt to limit the rights of the recipients of the
Larger Work over the Covered Software. If the Larger Work is distributed as
source code, then the Source Code Form of the Covered Software must be
distributed under this License; if the Larger Work is distributed only in
Executable Form, the Covered Software in Executable Form must be made
available under the terms of Section 2.4.

