rights under this License for the Source Code Form of the Covered Software.

3.2. Distribution of Source Code Form

You may distribute the Source Code Form of Covered Software under the
terms of this License.

3.3. Secondary Licenses

Notwithstanding Section 3.1, a Contributor may choose to make Covered
